      • getAlertReleasedToggle

        public final boolean getAlertReleasedToggle()
        Transient runtime information: return if the alert has been released or canceled.
        Note: this information is transient and not stored inside the XML configuration data.
        Returns:
        true if the alert has been released, or false if the alert has been canceled (or never was released).
